<font color="#FF0000">UN-CONSCIENCE LOGIC?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Oct 23 14:02:37 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Is it all a matter of personal conscience?<br><br>
Only if you have a conscience.<br><br>
Let's see what is going on here:<br><br>
Spatz #1 was called an imposter by Spatz #2 on this site.<br><br>
Spatz #3 claimed to me by e-mail that he was the real Spatz. <br>
&quot;Laying in front of trains was done up at the Oakland Draft Induction Stage and definately not my style of protesting.&quot;<br><br>
Cook has found Spatz #0, verifying Spatz #1 which I verified, contradicting the Spatz #2 and Spatz #3 claim that he did not lie on the tracks, etc. <br><br>
Spatz #0 says he lied on the tracks, etc., and so does Spatz #1.<br><br>
Spatz #2 and Spatz #3 says he did not lie on the tracks, etc.<br><br>
Spatz #0 predates Spatz #1 and Spatz #2 and Spatz #3 by 2 1/2 months.<br><br>
If Spatz #0 is the real Spatz, then Spatz #2 and #3 is fake.<br><br>
If Spatz #1 is the real Spatz, then Spatz #2 and #3 is fake.<br><br>
If Spatz #2 is the real Spatz, then Spatz #0 and Spatz #1 is fake, and Spatz #3 may or may not be fake.<br><br>
If Spatz #3 is the real Spatz, then Spatz #0 and Spatz #1 is fake, and Spatz #2 may or may not be fake.<br><br>
We do not know if Spatz #2 is Spatz #3.<br><br>
If Spatz #2 and Spatz #3 may or may not be independently fake, then Spatz #0 and Spatz #1 may or may not be dependently real.<br><br>
Therefore, with a high degree of certainty,<br><br>
Real = Fake, no matter which Spatz says what.<br><br>
..and<br><br>
Real - Fake = 0<br><br>
...which is really where we are at.<br><br>
On other posts, where anon # -1 and anon # -2  which Spatz #00 and Spatz #000 claims were not real, Spatz #0 and Spatz #1 may or may not be real, as well. We do not know at all if Spatz #2 and/or Spatz #3 is Spatz #00 and/or Spatz #000.<br><br>
Making sure I remain intellectual and unemotional, I have presented this original work of reasoning to make the point that anyone posting as some form of Spatz or denied by some form of Spatz as anorther form of Spatz should be ignored because you just don't know who or what is real, and in the interest of my sanity, because I took the time to get a headache trying to figure out that there was nothing real to figure out. It is all a fake!<br><br>
We will need a green pointy eared friend if this stuff continues!<br><br>

